<p><b>How to reset AC dodge caravan?</b> You can find three buttons on the left in the Dodge Caravan conditioning controls. Press and hold the topmost and the bottom buttons. While the top AC button regulates the rear wiper, the bottom one regulates the washer fluid of the rear wiper. Now check the AC light; it should illuminate and flash.</p>
